===Etymology 2===
Coined by [[w:Lewis Carroll|Lewis Carroll]] in [[s:Through The Looking Glass (And What Alice Found There)|Through The Looking Glass]] to describe the words he coined in [[w:Jabberwocky|Jabberwocky]].

